{
  "stem": "2723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I had created a dream world for myself, and I realize on looking back that my sort of ability to cope, physically, was because I lived in another world, as did probably my sister.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Our worlds were different, but we created that-- that sanctuary for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there was already encroachment from one world into the other.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We could not sustain ourselves much with what was our safety valve.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were terrified, and we sensed that our host and his wife became very nervous.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Once they knew that they were responsible, there was a definite feeling that we could sense of their nervousness, and we decided to call the second string.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We called this doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Actually, Gustav went to tell him that we were-- he admitted that he had been harboring us, and the message was that the choice was ours to make.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There is a possibility for us to hide.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The man was a member of a tennis club, which no longer was in use because the weather was getting cold.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was a pavilion there, and the pavilion was fully equipped for guests.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He would make sure that we would-- would have food for a week, that we had plenty of toy material and books, and we were getting very, very carried away about all the carrots.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that he would find a way of seeing us once a week.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We would be certainly left to our own devices, but we would have much more freedom within that confined situation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I think it was my decision to make the move.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't remember what my sister felt about it, but I just couldn't bear it any longer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I was shattered that my mother was taken away, and I made the decision.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
